<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٣ <span class="c1">"٧/٣٨٣"</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٤ لييست في <span class="c1">"ح"</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>